<<SetCharacterExpression "SunitaMadam" "Serious">>
SunitaMadam: We'll see, boy. We'll see if this intellectual curiosity is genuine or just a performance designed to impress adults.

<<SetCharacterExpression "SunitaMadam" "Serious">>
